<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= @subject %></title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #292524;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
    }
    
    /* Admin Container - matching admin design system */
    .admin-container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    
    .admin-container-header {
      padding: 20px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      background-color: #fff7ed;
    }
    
    .admin-container-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin: 0 0 4px 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    .admin-container-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #ea580c;
      margin: 0;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    .admin-container-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    
    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #7e2a0c;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .content-section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    
    .content-section p {
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .content-section ul {
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .content-section li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    
    /* Welcome Benefits */
    .welcome-benefits {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .welcome-benefits h3 {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    
    .welcome-benefits ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }
    
    .welcome-benefits li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #ea580c;
    }
    
    /* CTA Button */
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-primary {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #f54900;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: background-color 0.15s ease-in-out;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
    }
    
    .admin-btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #ca3500;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    
    .footer-link {
      color: #ea580c;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .footer-link:hover {
      color: #ca3500;
    }
    
    .signature {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #374151;
    }
    
    .signature-name {
      color: #7e2a0c;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .newsletter-info {
      background-color: #fff7ed;
      border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    
    .newsletter-info p {
      color: #ea580c;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="admin-container">
      <div class="admin-container-header">
        <div class="brand-logo">Mang Crinkle</div>
        <h1 class="admin-container-title">Welcome to the Family!</h1>
        <p class="admin-container-subtitle">Get ready for the most delicious Filipino treats</p>
      </div>

      <div class="admin-container-content">
        <div class="content-section">
          <p>Hello <%= @customer_name %>,</p>
          
          <% if @body %>
            <p><%= simple_format(@body) %></p>
          <% else %>
            <p>Welcome to the Mang Crinkle family! We're thrilled to have you join our community of Filipino food lovers and dessert enthusiasts.</p>
            
            <p>Get ready to experience the authentic taste of traditional Filipino crinkle cookies, made with love using time-honored recipes passed down through generations.</p>
          <% end %>
          
          <div class="welcome-benefits">
            <h3>As a Mang Crinkle family member, you'll enjoy:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Early access to new flavors and seasonal treats</li>
              <li>Exclusive discounts and special offers</li>
              <li>Behind-the-scenes stories from our kitchen</li>
              <li>Traditional Filipino baking tips and recipes</li>
              <li>Priority customer support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="content-section">
            <h3 style="color: #7e2a0c; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">What's Next?</h3>
            <p>Start exploring our delicious selection of authentic Filipino crinkle cookies, from classic favorites to exciting seasonal varieties.</p>
            <p>Keep an eye on your inbox for special offers, new flavor announcements, and exclusive content just for our family members!</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="<%= Rails.application.routes.url_helpers.products_url(host: Rails.application.config.action_mailer.default_url_options[:host]) %>" class="admin-btn-primary">Start Shopping</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="newsletter-info">
            <p><strong>Stay Connected:</strong> Follow us on social media for daily updates, behind-the-scenes content, and mouth-watering photos of our latest creations!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
          <p>This welcome email was sent to: <%= @user.email %></p>
          <p>Questions? Reply to this email or contact us at <%= company_email %></p>
          
          <div class="signature">
            <p>With love and fresh-baked goodness,<br>
            <span class="signature-name">The Mang Crinkle Team</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 